"2 cups sliced seeded watermelon","2 cups sliced seeded honeydew melon","1/3 cup very thinly vertically sliced red onion","1  serrano pepper, very thinly sliced","2  ripe nectarines, pitted and sliced","1/4 teaspoon kosher salt","3 tablespoons fresh lemon juice","2 tablespoons olive oil","1 1/2 tablespoons honey","4 cups arugula","1/4 cup torn fresh mint leaves","3 ounces prosciutto, very thinly sliced","1/2 ounce pecorino Romano cheese, shaved"